        <updateDate>2018-05-04T16:07:35Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Making Rural America Count Act </b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the Department of Agriculture from including incarcerated prison populations when determining eligibility or the levels of assistance for rural development programs. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
