        <title>Making Rural America Count Act</title>
      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To provide that determinations of eligibility and level of assistance for rural development programs shall be made without regard to incarcerated prisoner populations.</title>
      </item>
